OL,7,FAn explosion and fire at an illegal
OL,8,Foil refinery site in Nigeria has
OL,9,Fkilled at least 30 people, including
OL,10,Fa pregnant woman, a local community
OL,11,Fleader said.
OL,13,FIllegal oil refining is common in the
OL,14,Foil-rich Niger Delta region of the
OL,15,Fcountry as impoverished locals tap
OL,16,Fpipelines to make fuel to sell for a
OL,17,Fprofit.
OL,19,FThe practice, which can be as basic
OL,20,Fas boiling crude oil in drums to
OL,21,Fextract fuel, is often deadly.
